      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "TO speak to the union men in the\nservice.\n\n\nApparently the strikers are but\nlittle awed. Many of the pickets de-\nclare that they will pay no attention\nwhatever to the order.\n\n\nFive non-unionists arrived last\nnight In charge of the runs given up\nby the strikers The pickets were\nsuccessful in communicating with\nthem, and as a result they walked\nout and Joined the strikers. 1t is be-\nlieved that this is what precipitated\nthe Injunction."
    }
  ]
